still don't have a space.

01:31:08.680 --> 01:31:10.955
Actually, I don't think
that will be a problem.

01:31:12.120 --> 01:31:15.590
How would you like to establish
a permanent dance center,

01:31:15.680 --> 01:31:17.238
here at the Bijou?

01:31:17.320 --> 01:31:18.309
(CHUCKLES)

01:31:19.280 --> 01:31:20.315
You're serious?

01:31:20.400 --> 01:31:22.470
The community
needs this place.

01:31:22.560 --> 01:31:24.835
That's great, but what
made you change your mind?

01:31:25.640 --> 01:31:29.633
Consider it
a charitable gesture.

01:31:29.720 --> 01:31:32.553
Yeah. Her company wants
to have the appearance

01:31:32.640 --> 01:31:33.629
of being good people.

01:31:33.720 --> 01:31:34.709
(ALL CHUCKLE)

01:31:36.280 --> 01:31:38.714
Well, whatever the reason,
thank you.

01:31:39.800 --> 01:31:40.789
MELEA: Uh...

01:31:40.880 --> 01:31:44.953
Except I'd like to ask
for a favor, please.

01:31:45.280 --> 01:31:46.395
Which is?

01:31:46.880 --> 01:31:50.395
I'd like to name it after my
mother and 'Shani's brother.

01:31:50.880 --> 01:31:52.472
All right, yeah.

01:31:52.560 --> 01:31:53.959
MS. LEE: Done.
MELEA: Thank you.

01:31:54.040 --> 01:31:55.109
You're welcome.

01:31:55.200 --> 01:31:56.428
Yeah!

01:31:58.400 --> 01:31:59.799
Are you okay?

01:32:03.400 --> 01:32:04.469
Thank you.

